As we get ready for kick-off tomorrow, here is our code leading into the 2025 season. This is our 2024 code updated with beta releases of vendor reps.

github.com

GitHub - burde1jb/2025-FRC-4327-Test-Code

Contribute to burde1jb/2025-FRC-4327-Test-Code development by creating an account on GitHub.

Our code is command based, uses CTRE’s Tuner X for swerve drivetrain code, limelight for vision, and pathplanner for autos. All constants are in one “RobotConstants.java” file and referenced throughout the code.

Good luck everyone!
